---
import DefaultLayout from '../layouts/DefaultLayout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
---
<DefaultLayout title="Volleyball Coaching Bible" description="A complete club coaching standards manual.">
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 md:py-20">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-stone-900 mb-4">
      Coaching Bible
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-stone-600 max-w-2xl mb-10">
      An LLM-maintained volleyball coaching reference and club standards manual — 60+ coach profiles,
      43 schools of thought, 101 drills, 9 age-guides, 8 cue dictionaries, 10 tryout rubrics, 25 practice plans.
    </p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-12">
      <a href={`${base}/manual/`} class="block p-6 rounded-lg border border-stone-200 hover:border-orange-400 hover:bg-orange-50 no-underline transition-colors">
        <div class="kicker mb-2">Manual</div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-xl font-bold mb-1 text-stone-900">Club coaching standards</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">Per-age technical milestones, canonical cues, drill picks, tryout rubrics — the four-question loop for every age.</p>
      </a>
      <a href={`${base}/drills/`} class="block p-6 rounded-lg border border-stone-200 hover:border-orange-400 hover:bg-orange-50 no-underline transition-colors">
        <div class="kicker mb-2">Drills</div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-xl font-bold mb-1 text-stone-900">Filterable drill catalog</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">101 drills filterable by skill, phase, age, duration, team size. The "find me a drill in 10 seconds" entry point.</p>
      </a>
      <a href={`${base}/library/`} class="block p-6 rounded-lg border border-stone-200 hover:border-orange-400 hover:bg-orange-50 no-underline transition-colors">
        <div class="kicker mb-2">Library</div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-xl font-bold mb-1 text-stone-900">Reference encyclopedia</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">Skill hubs, techniques, systems, positions, schools of thought, methodology hubs, sources.</p>
      </a>
      <a href={`${base}/search/`} class="block p-6 rounded-lg border border-stone-200 hover:border-orange-400 hover:bg-orange-50 no-underline transition-colors">
        <div class="kicker mb-2">Search</div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-xl font-bold mb-1 text-stone-900">Full-text search</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">Pagefind-indexed. Search every page, every cue, every drill.</p>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="text-sm text-stone-500 border-t border-stone-200 pt-6">
      <p>Built on 1100+ markdown pages of citation-disciplined coaching synthesis. Sources span Karch Kiraly's <em>Championship Volleyball</em>, Hugh McCutcheon's <em>Championship Behaviors</em>, Mike Lingenfelter's Munciana camp library, the Art of Coaching Volleyball corpus (~520 articles), peer-reviewed sports-science research (50 papers), and 15+ definitive coaching books — synthesized with neutral attribution across schools of thought.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</DefaultLayout>
